<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="a-little">a little</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-a-bit">1.<strong>[表示肯定含义] 少量；有点儿 (a bit)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There was only a little applause when I left the stage.
我离开舞台时，只有稀稀落落的一点儿掌声。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Are you sometimes a little tired and sleepy in the early afternoon? 
你是否有时刚到下午就感到有点儿累，并且想睡觉？</p><footer>2008 四川</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He knows a little of everything. 
他样样都懂一点儿。</p></div>

<p>注: a little可修饰不可数名词、形容词、副词和动词等。  </p></div>